SELECT
                MAX(id),
                SUM(value)
            FROM
                scalar_tap_receipts
            WHERE
                allocation_id = $1
                AND id <= $2
                AND signer_address IN (SELECT unnest($3::text[]))
                AND timestamp_ns > $4

SELECT
                MAX(id),
                SUM(value),
                COUNT(*)
            FROM
                scalar_tap_receipts
            WHERE
                allocation_id = $1
                AND signer_address IN (SELECT unnest($2::text[]))
                AND timestamp_ns > $3
